data.text: Footy is starting to hot up and the AFL Record has all the news, features and stats to keep you informed while you are at the game. The Round 6 edition includes a special Anzac tribute to former League stars Ted Whitten, Kevin Sheedy and Royce Hart who put their football careers on hold to enlist for National Service. And we honour the fallen with a list of known players and umpires who made the ultimate sacrifice while serving their country. Don’t miss regular features including Answer Man with our stats experts, player profiles as well as team lists for all 18 clubs. The AFL Record is brought to you by Four ‘N Twenty – make sure you grab your copy this week, still only $5! The Round 6 print edition will be on sale at all venues for $5. It is also on sale in Victoria at newsagents, Coles and Coles Express. The digital edition is available online via SEN.com.au. To subscribe to the AFL Record, visit aflrecord.com.au
